Fashion

Makeup
Course

This tutorial will
teach you:

  • how to blend eyeshadows like a pro
  • different ways of applying loose eyeshadow pigments
  • the right order of eyeshadows application according to its color
  • which tools are necessary for a proper eye makeup
  • how to bring out eyes without applying a classic eyeliner
  • peculiarities of working with a lower eyelid
To complete course Evening Makeup you should also complete lessons: Perfect (everyday) Makeup, Evening Makeup, Bridal Makeup.
